---
title: Creamy Cajun Chicken & Leek Fusilli  with Double Cheddar & Garden Salad
description: You can’t go wrong with a creamy pasta dish, it’s a hit every time! This one has chicken, leek and lots of Cheddar cheese to really amp up the yum-factor - you’ll have a table full of empty bowls and smiling faces in no time.
